Description: Based on P. N. Mendes- M. Jakob- A. Garc√≠a-Silva- and C. Bizer. DBpedia Spotlight: shedding light on the web of documents. In Proc. of the 7th Int. Conf. on Semantic Systems- 2011.It contains 60 natural language sentences from ten different New York Times articles with overall 249 annotated DBpedia entities- i. e. the entities are not explicitely bound to mentions within the texts- which causes a certain lack of clarity. Therefore- we (in all conscience) retroactively have allocated the entities to their positions within the texts.The entities dbp:Markup_Language and dbp:PBC_CSKA_Moscow could not be linked in the texts- since there was also a more specific entity enlisted occupying their solely possible location- e. g. hypertext markup language has been annotated with dbp:HTML rather than dbp:Markup_language.
